From e9bfe5eec9626fa7be26d1a10733021555a96835 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Salis Dev <dev@salis.app>
Date: Wed, 27 May 2026 23:16:16 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(storefront): migrate to Next.js 15 with Feature-Driven
 Architecture
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Replace Vite with Next.js 15 App Router
- Feature-Driven structure: features/products, cart, checkout
- Custom Hooks: useProducts, useCart, useCheckout
- Salis design identity: Warm White + Coral + Dark Navy
- Full TypeScript — zero any usage
- Salis CSS design tokens via CSS variables
- Dark mode via data-theme
- ProductCard, ProductGrid with skeleton loading
- CartDrawer, CheckoutModal, Navbar components
